trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref uid="langword_csharp_try" name="try" href=""></xref> block with any number of <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""></xref> clauses and, optionally, a <xref uid="langword_csharp_finally" name="finally" href=""></xref> block.
trans-unit.target: 나타냅니다는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_try" name="try" href=""> </xref> 개수에 관계 없이 사용 하 여 블록 <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""> </xref> 절 및 필요에 따라 한 <xref uid="langword_csharp_finally" name="finally" href=""> </xref> 블록입니다.

trans-unit.source: CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement can be used to represent a `try/``catch` block of code.
trans-unit.target: CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement 나타내는 데 사용할 수는 `try/``catch` 코드 블록입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.TryStatements%2A> property contains the statements to execute within a `try` block.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.TryStatements%2A>속성 내에서 실행할 문을 포함 한 `try` 블록.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.TryStatements%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.CatchClauses%2A> property contains the `catch` clauses to handle caught exceptions.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.CatchClauses%2A>속성에 포함 된 `catch` 절이 검색 되었습니다 예외를 처리 합니다.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.CatchClauses%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.FinallyStatements%2A> property contains the statements to execute within a `finally` block.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.FinallyStatements%2A>속성 내에서 실행할 문을 포함 한 `finally` 블록.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement.FinallyStatements%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Not all languages support `try/catch` blocks.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 지원 하지 않는 언어도 `try/catch` 블록입니다.

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A> method with the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport?displayProperty=fullName> flag to determine whether a code generator supports `try/catch` blocks.
trans-unit.target: 호출 된 <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A>메서드는 <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport?displayProperty=fullName>코드 생성기에서 지원 하는지 여부를 확인 하는 플래그 `try/catch` 블록.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A>

trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTryCatchFinallyStatement"> </xref> 시도 대 한 지정한 문을 사용 하 여 클래스 및 catch 절.

trans-unit.target: 배열을 <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeStatement"> </xref> 시도 문을 나타내는 개체입니다.
